        '<p><strong>Every Life We Find Each Other</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every life we find each other is the third book of Brain L. Weiss &ndash; a famous psychiatrist. He had previously written two books: the first being Obsession from a Previous Life, the book describing the true story of a young patient along with hypnotic treatments about past lives that changed both the author&#39;s and her lives. The book has sold well worldwide with over 2 million copies printed and translated into more than 20 languages. The second book Through Time into Healing describes what the author has learned about the healing potential of pre-life recursive therapy. In the book are real people&#39;s stories. But the most compelling story is in the third book.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Every lifetime we find each other speaks of soul-to-soul souls who are permanently connected with each other with love, always seeing each other again and again, over and over again. We find and recognize how our memories are, and then make decisions that change our own lives as the most important and emotional moments in each person&#39;s life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Destiny will lead the way for the souls of the soul to reunite. We&#39;ll meet them. But deciding what to do afterwards is everyone&#39;s freedom of choice. A wrong choice or a missed opportunity can lead to extreme loneliness and anguish. And a right choice, an opportunity to be seized can bring profound happiness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What the author writes in the book is recorded from medical records, recording tapes and memory. Only the name and a few small details are changed to keep the security. This is a story of destiny and hope. This is a story that happens silently every day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On this day of the year, someone listened.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Water-like soul</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Falling from heaven</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sky like smog</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Then back to the land.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Endless chain of patrols.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Goethe</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product prices on Tiki are inclusive of taxes under applicable law. However, depending on the type of product or method, delivery address, additional costs such as shipping fees, bulky cargo surcharges, ...</p>\r\n',
