        '<p><strong>Rainbow Warrior (Re-2020)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of Indonesia&#39;s<br />\r\n<br />\r\nmost influential works &quot;Poor Mr. Harfan and Ms. Mus brought me the most beautiful childhood, the most beautiful friendship, and the rich soul, something invaluable, even more valuable than the longings of dreams. I may be wrong, but in my opinion, this is really the breath of education and the soul of a place called a school.&quot;<br />\r\n- (Excerpt)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n***<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOn the opening day, thanks to the last-minute appearance of the intellectually inelected boy Harun, The Muhammadiyah School is lucky to escape the danger of closure. But where will the dream of teaching and learning in that Islamic school go, when the saggy school seems ready to collapse at any moment, when the threat of closure from the education inspector is always hovering over his head, when ferocious excavator machines are waiting to smash the school to detect the tin circuit...? And whether the Rainbow Warriors&#39; passion for learning is enough to conquer the forty-day cycling day, then the crocodile lagoon at the time of the cannibals, not to mention the enchantment from the deadly adventures called by the mysterious wizard<br />\r\n<br />\r\non Pirate Island, and the wise temptation from the stunted coins earned thanks to the full-time work of the Rainbow Warrior has both love in the morning of school and mischievous jokes, both tears and laughter &ndash; a true picture of the pit. , a touchy literary work that most deeply conveys the true meaning of being a teacher, a student, and learning.<br />\r\nThe work has sold over five million copies, translated into 26 languages, as one of the best representatives of modern Indonesian<br />\r\nliterature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product prices on Tiki are inclusive of taxes under applicable law. However, depending on the type of product or method, delivery address, additional costs such as shipping fees, bulky cargo surcharges, ...</p>\r\n',
