        '<p><strong>Morisaki Bookstore Dreams</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Deceived by his lover, Takako quits his job and falls into a series of sleeping days to hide from sadness. Then, a phone call from her uncle of 10 years without seeing her woke her from a dream. Takako agrees to go to the bookstore at half-time to help him just to please his mother. But beyond imagination, waiting for her is the old Morisaki bookstore with the world of thousands of books contained in her both time and history. The book healed the wounds in your heart.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>And more than that, Takako finds many new and interesting things that she has never known before. The story is gentle but deep, especially for those who have a hobby of collecting antique books.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product prices on Tiki are inclusive of taxes under applicable law. However, depending on the type of product or method, delivery address, additional costs such as shipping fees, bulky cargo surcharges, ...</p>\r\n',
