        ',https://salt.tikicdn.com/cache/w444/ts/product/4f/a9/27/d13ea6c22896fe3782d7051fa146f98a.jpg', 139500, 120,
        '<p>Two Fates (Cardboard) is a book that is not merely a novel that can be considered &quot;biblical&quot; for those who do not easily accept the trail, the book is loved by many readers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot; Two fates&quot; shakes every brave heart, it can change your whole life. Reading this book, you will be dominated by the personality of the two main characters, either you are Kane, or will be Abel, unmistakable. And that will make you see yourself.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you love this work, one will see your interesting personality and soul!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;If there is a Nobel Prize in storytelling, it will definitely go to Archer.&quot; - Daily Telegraph</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Two Fates&quot; (Kane &amp; Abel) is the story of two men seeking glory. William Kane is the son of a famous millionaire on American soil, raised in the silk velvet of the upper class world. Wladek Koskiewicz was an unknown child who was picked up by the animal trapper&#39;s family. One was set to become a banker when he was growing up, the other immigly to the U.S. with a delegation of poor people.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Over sixty years with many fluctuations, two people with ambitions to build their destiny. &quot;Two Fates&quot; is about burning desires, gestures, feuds, adventure paths, world realism and corners that fascinate the reader with condensed words, two parallel storylines built delicately from the smallest details.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Product prices on Tiki are inclusive of taxes under applicable law. However, depending on the type of product or method, delivery address, additional costs such as shipping fees, bulky cargo surcharges, ...</p>\r\n',
